summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 81W, page 188-a of the Official land Use Map to rezone the property located at 9245 Rainier Avenue South from Lowrise-2 (L-2) to Commercial 1 with a thirty-foot height limitation (C1/30') and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Larry Vinson and South East Effective Development, C. F. 299584)
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
